  _characterName: Emma
  _personalityInfo: 'Intelligence and Resourcefulness: Emma is highly intelligent
    and resourceful. She possesses a sharp analytical mind and is quick to adapt
    to new situations. Her ability to think on her feet makes her an invaluable asset
    to the detective.

    

    Bubbly and Supportive: Despite her analytical
    prowess, Emma has a bubbly and friendly personality. She is approachable and
    always maintains a positive attitude, which helps to alleviate tension during
    the investigation.

    

    Tech-Savvy: In the futuristic sci-fi setting
    of the game, Emma is exceptionally tech-savvy. She has an in-depth understanding
    of cybernetics, AI systems, and hacking techniques, which proves useful when
    dealing with the advanced technology in the case.'
  _behaviourInfo: 'Research and Information Gathering: Emma excels in conducting
    research and gathering information. She often assists the detective by digging
    up background details on suspects, locations, and technological aspects related
    to the case.

    

    Supportive Role: During interrogations and conversations
    with NPCs, Emma offers subtle hints and suggestions to guide the player when
    they seem stuck or confused. Her assistance keeps the investigation moving forward
    smoothly.

    

    Hacking Expertise: Emma''s tech-savvy nature extends to
    her ability to hack into secure systems and databases when necessary, helping
    the detective access vital information and uncover hidden clues.

    

    Moral
    Compass: Emma serves as a moral compass for the detective, reminding them to
    consider ethical dilemmas and consequences when making decisions during the investigation.
    Her presence helps maintain a sense of justice and fairness in their actions.

    

    Team
    Collaboration: Emma fosters a collaborative atmosphere, encouraging teamwork
    between herself and the detective. She values open communication and brainstorming
    sessions to piece together the puzzle.'
  _motivationsInfo: 'Passion for Investigation: Emma''s primary motivation is her
    passion for investigation and solving mysteries. She genuinely enjoys her role
    as the detective''s assistant and is committed to uncovering the truth behind
    complex cases.

    

    Supporting the Detective: Emma is deeply devoted
    to the detective, viewing them as a mentor and role model. Her motivation includes
    helping the detective succeed and providing crucial assistance in solving cases.

    

    Curiosity
    and Learning: Emma is constantly seeking opportunities to learn and expand her
    knowledge. She sees each case as a chance to acquire new skills and insights,
    making her an ever-improving and indispensable partner to the detective.'
